_sText:
A port of surf_bikini_bottom originally introduced to CS:GO as a full bright map with no sort of lighting.

This port brings lighting, new ramp textures, particles, and sounds! Revamped for release on KSF, we hope this map brings you as much nostalgia as it does Jooce and I.Â 

No major changes on the map pertaining to the original route on CS:GO servers - some crutch ramps have been removed but all skips stay the same.
